FeedPackage.Description:
Complex C# library for Firebase Realtime Database built on top of Firebase REST API. Among others it supports following:
* Offline storage * Querying using available filters * Passing in authentication token * Streaming online changes * Directly Posting / Putting / Patching online data
Streaming changes (both online and offline) are done using Reactive Extensions.
